 jer po taj nacionalni osjećaj,

1131
00:42:57,060 --> 00:42:58,840
 koliko god ga se pokušavalo

1132
00:42:58,840 --> 00:43:01,320
 ugušiti, koliko god ga se pokušavalo

1133
00:43:01,320 --> 00:43:03,280
 nivelirati, pretvoriti sve

1134
00:43:03,280 --> 00:43:05,320
 u nekakav opći, evropski,

1135
00:43:05,320 --> 00:43:07,660
 zajednički sentiment i osjećaj,

1136
00:43:07,740 --> 00:43:09,200
 to neće ići, dakle, to jednostavno

1137
00:43:09,200 --> 00:43:10,360
 ne funkcionira na taj način.

1138
00:43:10,360 --> 00:43:11,500
 Sad, pavljeste, mi doslovno smo

1139
00:43:11,500 --> 00:43:12,560
 isključeni iz pregovora,

1140
00:43:12,560 --> 00:43:13,840
 ratuje se na evropskom tlu.

1141
00:43:13,840 --> 00:43:16,780
 Mislim, to je onako malo ponižavajuće,

1142
00:43:16,780 --> 00:43:17,020
 je li da?

1143
00:43:17,020 --> 00:43:19,340
 Malo je ponižavajuće, ali mi sami smo

1144
00:43:19,340 --> 00:43:21,400
 krivi što smo se doveli

1145
00:43:21,400 --> 00:43:22,300
 u takvu situaciju.

1146
00:43:22,300 --> 00:43:22,580
 Da.

1147
00:43:22,580 --> 00:43:25,420
 Gospodine, je ono će teško je podviđati.

1148
00:43:25,420 --> 00:43:27,240
 Sve mislite subijno Ukrajine,

1149
00:43:27,240 --> 00:43:28,960
 sad moramo je se da takrat, mislim.

1150
00:43:28,960 --> 00:43:30,860
 Moji su simpatije na ukrajinskoj strani,

1151
00:43:30,980 --> 00:43:32,820
 O tome nema apsolutno nikakve dvojbe.

1152
00:43:32,820 --> 00:43:34,880
 Ja bi želio da Ukrajina iziđe

1153
00:43:34,880 --> 00:43:37,960
 iz rata, dakle, teritorijalno neokrnjena

1154
00:43:37,960 --> 00:43:39,220
 i politički stažna.

1155
00:43:39,220 --> 00:43:41,900
 Bojim se da se to tako neće dogoditi,

1156
00:43:41,900 --> 00:43:45,920
 ali uvijek treba biti svjesan

1157
00:43:45,920 --> 00:43:47,460
 da je ono što se govori

1158
00:43:47,460 --> 00:43:48,880
 kao nekakva opća formula

1159
00:43:48,880 --> 00:43:50,040
 da je nepravedan mir

1160
00:43:50,040 --> 00:43:53,220
 je zametak novoga sukoba,

1161
00:43:53,220 --> 00:43:53,860
 novoga rata.

1162
00:43:53,860 --> 00:43:55,480
 Dakle, nije bilo slučajno

1163
00:43:55,480 --> 00:43:57,140
 kad su dalekovidni ljudi

1164
00:43:57,140 --> 00:43:59,100
 čuši kako glasi

1165
00:43:59,100 --> 00:44:00,200
 versajski sporazum.

1166
00:44:00,200 --> 00:44:01,240
 Dakle, ja sad citiram

1167
00:44:01,240 --> 00:44:03,760
 francuskog maršala,

1168
00:44:03,760 --> 00:44:05,180
 jednoga, dakle, koji je na vijest

1169
00:44:05,180 --> 00:44:06,860
 o sklapanju versajskog sporazuma,

1170
00:44:06,860 --> 00:44:10,080
 dakle, koji je Njemačku desetkovao

1171
00:44:10,080 --> 00:44:11,600
 nakon prvog svjetskog rata,

1172
00:44:11,600 --> 00:44:12,840
 kazao ovo nije mir,

1173
00:44:12,840 --> 00:44:15,160
 nego je primjer je na 20 godina.

1174
00:44:15,160 --> 00:44:16,880
 I pokazalo se savršeno, precizno,

1175
00:44:16,880 --> 00:44:18,200
 dakle, jer ste jednostavno

1176
00:44:18,200 --> 00:44:19,880
 povrijedili, ponizili jedan narod

1177
00:44:19,880 --> 00:44:23,380
 u kojem će tinjati nezadovojstvo

1178
00:44:23,380 --> 00:44:24,400
 dok to nezadovojstvo

1179
00:44:24,400 --> 00:44:25,420
 jednom ne rumpira,

1180
00:44:25,420 --> 00:44:27,380
 dok jednom, dakle, ne iziđe na svjetla dana

1181
00:44:27,380 --> 00:44:29,760
 i ne bih želio, dakle, da

1182
00:44:29,760 --> 00:44:32,420
 možda mi to nećemo doživjeti,

1183
00:44:32,420 --> 00:44:33,580
 ali ne bih želio da to dožive

1184
00:44:33,580 --> 00:44:34,680
 moja djeca, moji unuci,

1185
00:44:34,680 --> 00:44:35,320
 da dožive

1186
00:44:35,320 --> 00:44:39,500
 posljedice onoga što se možda

1187
00:44:39,500 --> 00:44:40,840
 dogodi danas.

1188
00:44:40,840 --> 00:44:42,600
 Međutim, mi smo premali,

1189
00:44:42,600 --> 00:44:43,720
 dakle, mi kao Hrvati,

1190
00:44:43,720 --> 00:44:45,220
 Hrvatski narod i Hrvatska država,

1191
00:44:45,220 --> 00:44:47,060
 mi smo premali da bi smo u tome mogli

1192
00:44:47,060 --> 00:44:48,760
 presudno uđati.

1193
00:44:48,840 --> 00:44:50,000
 Bili smo malo glasni,

1194
00:44:50,000 --> 00:44:52,360
 ali evo sad primijetim i premijer i predsjednik Šut.

1195
00:44:52,360 --> 00:44:55,940
 Da, jer su, dakle, bili,

1196
00:44:55,940 --> 00:44:58,380
 pogotovo predsjednik vlade je bio zagrizao,

1197
00:44:58,380 --> 00:45:01,380
 zaloga je veći od onoga koji može progutati,

1198
00:45:01,380 --> 00:45:04,140
 pa je sad shvatio, dakle, da se mora curikati.

1199
00:45:04,140 --> 00:45:06,000
 Jer ovo je, ajmo reć,

1200
00:45:06,000 --> 00:45:07,680
 ispravi teme slobodno,

1201
00:45:07,920 --> 00:45:10,860
 vrlo direktna, ali i ružna poruka

1202
00:45:10,860 --> 00:45:11,740
 jedne Amerike,

1203
00:45:11,740 --> 00:45:14,120
 Ukrajincima i Savjeznicima.

1204
00:45:14,120 --> 00:45:16,440
 Ono, pay per view,

1205
00:45:16,440 --> 00:45:17,800
 plati pa te brani.

1206
00:45:17,800 --> 00:45:18,300
 Tako je.

1207
00:45:18,300 --> 00:45:20,380
 Nije da mi nismo znali da je

1208
00:45:20,380 --> 00:45:22,740
 i Bajdenova administracija imala tu interesa,

1209
00:45:22,740 --> 00:45:23,720
 svi uvijek imaju interesa,

1210
00:45:23,720 --> 00:45:25,400
 ali ovo je bilo ono direktno,

1211
00:45:25,400 --> 00:45:26,900
 ko bok su šakom u glavu.

1212
00:45:26,900 --> 00:45:28,340
 Ovo je bilo potpuno otvoreno

1213
00:45:28,340 --> 00:45:29,220
 i nedvosmisleno.

1214
00:45:29,220 --> 00:45:32,000
 Kako bi sad mi se trebali kao evropljeni ponašati?

1215
00:45:32,000 --> 00:45:34,920
 Nismo navikuli na taj način ophođenja,

1216
00:45:34,920 --> 00:45:36,380
 ali očito ćemo se morati navikavati,

1217
00:45:36,460 --> 00:45:37,480
 ono što ste u jednom trenutku

1218
00:45:37,480 --> 00:45:38,940
 u današnjem našem razgovoru kazali,

1219
00:45:38,940 --> 00:45:42,760
 prošlo vrijeme diplomacije u rukavicama.

1220
00:45:42,760 --> 00:45:45,880
 Jasno, dakle, to vrijeme je očito prošlo.

1221
00:45:45,880 --> 00:45:46,820
 Dakle, vraćamo se,

1222
00:45:46,820 --> 00:45:50,440
 jer bilo je prije 60-70 godina,

1223
00:45:50,440 --> 00:45:51,700
 slično tako vrijeme, dakle,

1224
00:45:51,700 --> 00:45:53,120
 u kojem su postojali diktati

1225
00:45:53,120 --> 00:45:54,280
 i u kojem se niste mogli

1226
00:45:54,280 --> 00:45:56,780
 pozvati ni na međunarodno pravo,

1227
00:45:56,780 --> 00:45:58,660
 ni na diplomatsko ophođenje,

1228
00:45:58,660 --> 00:45:59,960
 nego je vrijedila gola sila.

1229
00:45:59,960 --> 00:46:02,760
 Dakle, govorimo o vremenu konfrontacije

1230
00:46:02,760 --> 00:46:04,580
 koja je dovela do drugog svjetskog rata.

1231
00:46:04,580 --> 00:46:04,940
 Dakle,

1232
00:46:05,000 --> 00:46:08,580
 ponovno ulazimo u to razdoblje,

1233
00:46:08,580 --> 00:46:10,800
 nadajmo se da ono neće biti tako traumatično,

1234
00:46:10,800 --> 00:46:13,220
 da neće biti tako krvavo kao što je bilo ono.

1235
00:46:13,220 --> 00:46:15,260
 Da, kak bi rekli bakice na placu,

1236
00:46:15,260 --> 00:46:16,640
 čime ću platiti Americi,

1237
00:46:16,640 --> 00:46:17,280
 sve smo dali.

1238
00:46:17,280 --> 00:46:17,860
 Da, da.

1239
00:46:17,860 --> 00:46:18,760
 Mislim, tako,

1240
00:46:18,760 --> 00:46:20,520
 da, šerif, da, dobro,

1241
00:46:20,520 --> 00:46:21,800
 evo je njegov rekao, šerif je,

1242
00:46:21,800 --> 00:46:24,060
 vidit ćemo sad šta će biti.

1243
00:46:24,440 --> 00:46:26,920
 Kako biste mogli na našu regiju odrasiti?

1244
00:46:26,920 --> 00:46:29,940
 Sad, kad govorite regiju,

1245
00:46:29,940 --> 00:46:32,100
 ne govorite o Karlovačkoj regiji.

1246
00:46:32,100 --> 00:46:33,580
 Ne, ne, ne, nego u Hrvatskoj.

1247
00:46:33,580 --> 00:46:35,500
 Odnosno, području Bivše Jugoslavije.

1248
00:46:35,500 --> 00:46:38,800
 Dakle, ja bi prvo izbjegao taj termin uopći,

1249
00:46:38,800 --> 00:46:42,060
 dakle, jer ne vidim nikakva razloga da se mi uspoređujemo

1250
00:46:42,060 --> 00:46:43,320
 sa, ovaj,

1251
00:46:43,320 --> 00:46:45,440
 ono je područjeno koje je pripadalo

1252
00:46:45,440 --> 00:46:46,600
 Bivše Jugoslavije.

1253
00:46:46,600 --> 00:46:48,360
 Dakle, ne treba ni na koji način

1254
00:46:48,360 --> 00:46:51,080
 održavati predođbu o tome

1255
00:46:51,080 --> 00:46:52,320
 da je to nekakav jedinstveni,

1256
00:46:52,320 --> 00:46:54,700
 geopolitički, kulturni, civilizacijski prostor.

1257
00:46:54,700 --> 00:46:56,500
 To su države koje su nastale

1258
00:46:56,500 --> 00:46:59,140
 i koje će, po svemu sudeći,

1259
00:46:59,140 --> 00:47:00,860
 obstati, dakle, koji će samostalno

1260
00:47:00,860 --> 00:47:01,800
 kreirati svoju sudbinu.

1261
00:47:01,800 --> 00:47:03,840
 Zbog toga, kad mi se kaže regija,

1262
00:47:03,840 --> 00:47:05,260
 ja mislim na Zagrebačku regiju,

1263
00:47:05,260 --> 00:47:07,220
 Splitsku, Riječku, Osječku i tako dalje,

1264
00:47:07,220 --> 00:47:08,700
 ništa šire od toga.

1265
00:47:12,060 --> 00:47:14,980
 Ključni naš interes u Bosni i Hercegovine,

1266
00:47:14,980 --> 00:47:16,840
 dakle, jer je tamo glavnina,

1267
00:47:16,840 --> 00:47:19,540
 odnosno dobar dio hrvatskog naroda,

1268
00:47:19,540 --> 00:47:22,360
 dakle, koji je zapravo obespravljen,

1269
00:47:22,360 --> 00:47:26,660
 koji već godinama ili zapravo desetljećima

1270
00:47:26,660 --> 00:47:28,800
 ne uspjeva izabrati,

1271
00:47:28,800 --> 00:47:30,380
 ne dopuštamo se izabrati

1272
00:47:30,380 --> 00:47:32,040
 vlastite legitimne predstavnike

1273
00:47:32,040 --> 00:47:36,060
 i mislim da je naš nacionalni državni interes

1274
00:47:36,060 --> 00:47:37,560
 primarno, dakle, osiguranje

1275
00:47:37,560 --> 00:47:40,700
 položaje jednakopravnosti Hroata

1276
00:47:40,700 --> 00:47:42,160
 u Bosni i Hercegovini,

1277
00:47:42,160 --> 00:47:44,440
 a to je ujedno sredstvo kojim se ta država

1278
00:47:44,440 --> 00:47:46,180
 može održati na okupu,

1279
00:47:46,180 --> 00:47:48,220
 jer onog trenutka, dakle, kad njezini narodi,

1280
00:47:48,220 --> 00:47:50,220
 govorimo o tri konstitutivna naroda,

1281
00:47:50,220 --> 00:47:51,400
 kad oni nisu zadovoljni,

1282
00:47:51,400 --> 00:47:52,400
 kad se oni osjećaju,

1283
00:47:52,400 --> 00:47:53,400
 neki od njih,

1284
00:47:53,400 --> 00:47:55,620
 kad se osjećaju bespravljenim,

1285
00:47:55,620 --> 00:47:58,220
 to je zapravo otvaranje puta

1286
00:47:58,220 --> 00:48:00,760
 u nerede, u kaos

1287
00:48:00,760 --> 00:48:02,940
 i u disoluciju raspad te države.

1288
00:48:02,940 --> 00:48:04,140
 To je nešto što mislim da

1289
00:48:04,140 --> 00:48:06,380
 hrvatskome narodu ne bi odgovarilo,

1290
00:48:06,380 --> 00:48:07,740
 ne bi odgovarilo hrvatskoj državi.

1291
00:48:07,740 --> 00:48:11,220
 Mislim da će Srbija probati skolisito na uštad,

1292
00:48:11,220 --> 00:48:11,640
 recimo,

1293
00:48:11,640 --> 00:48:13,720
 da je Trumpovi administracije

1294
00:48:13,720 --> 00:48:15,180
 po pitanju Republike Srpske,

1295
00:48:15,180 --> 00:48:15,940
 da malo...

1296
00:48:15,940 --> 00:48:17,200
 Ja ne sumnjam da...

1297
00:48:17,200 --> 00:48:17,900
 Sad je vidljio,

1298
00:48:17,900 --> 00:48:18,820
 pardon, da je Vučić,

1299
00:48:18,820 --> 00:48:19,600
 ajmo reći,

1300
00:48:19,600 --> 00:48:20,400
 brislanski igrač.

1301
00:48:20,400 --> 00:48:22,000
 Ja ne sumnjam u to,

1302
00:48:22,000 --> 00:48:24,220
 da u Srbiji postoji takav interes

1303
00:48:24,220 --> 00:48:25,860
 i da je to zapravo dubinska želja

1304
00:48:25,860 --> 00:48:28,180
 velikog dijela Srpske ili Srbijanske.

1305
00:48:28,180 --> 00:48:29,600
 Srpske, dakle, kad govorim,

1306
00:48:29,600 --> 00:48:30,920
 ne samo one koji su u Srbiji,

1307
00:48:30,920 --> 00:48:31,740
 nego i uopće,

1308
00:48:31,740 --> 00:48:33,480
 dakle, srpske političke elite

1309
00:48:33,480 --> 00:48:35,220
 i u BiH i u Hrvatskoj.

1310
00:48:35,220 --> 00:48:36,620
 Dakle, svi bi oni zapravo htjeli

1311
00:48:36,620 --> 00:48:38,120
 prekrajanje granica,

1312
00:48:38,120 --> 00:48:38,960
 to je ono što je

1313
00:48:38,960 --> 00:48:40,620
 Patriar Srpske pravoslavne crkve

1314
00:48:40,620 --> 00:48:42,780
 podsjetio nas ne tako davno,

1315
00:48:42,780 --> 00:48:44,240
 dakle, da su granice promjenjive

1316
00:48:44,240 --> 00:48:46,600
 i da ne treba odustati od onoga

1317
00:48:46,600 --> 00:48:47,380
 što oni nazivaju

1318
00:48:47,380 --> 00:48:48,560
 zapadnim srpskim krajevima,

1319
00:48:48,560 --> 00:48:49,720
 odnosno srpskim svetom.

1320
00:48:49,720 --> 00:48:50,960
 Dakle, neće ti,

1321
00:48:50,960 --> 00:48:52,600
 te ambicije i te težnje

1322
00:48:52,600 --> 00:48:53,320
 neće prestati,

1323
00:48:53,440 --> 00:48:54,500
 međutim, mislim da smo mi

1324
00:48:54,500 --> 00:48:55,340
 dovoljno jake,

1325
00:48:55,340 --> 00:48:56,720
 da je Srbija dovoljno slaba,

1326
00:48:56,720 --> 00:48:58,560
 da bi tako nešto mogla realizirati.

1327
00:48:58,560 --> 00:48:59,680
 I nisam uvjeren da bi

1328
00:48:59,680 --> 00:49:01,920
 naišlo to na simpatije

1329
00:49:01,920 --> 00:49:04,620
 ni nove američke vlade.

1330
00:49:04,620 --> 00:49:06,120
 Dakle, vidjeli ste sada reakcije

1331
00:49:06,120 --> 00:49:07,600
 nakon presude

1332
00:49:07,600 --> 00:49:09,360
 Miloradu Dodiku,

1333
00:49:09,360 --> 00:49:10,540
 dakle, da je službeni

1334
00:49:10,540 --> 00:49:12,200
 Washington zapravo reagirao

1335
00:49:12,200 --> 00:49:13,900
 puno energičnije

1336
00:49:13,900 --> 00:49:14,440
 i puno nedvosmislenije

1337
00:49:14,440 --> 00:49:16,520
 nego što su reagirile

1338
00:49:16,520 --> 00:49:17,860
 evropske predstavnice,

1339
00:49:17,860 --> 00:49:19,200
 dakle, na Dodikove najave

1340
00:49:19,200 --> 00:49:22,480
 koraka koji bi doveli

1341
00:49:22,480 --> 00:49:23,100
 do slabljanja

1342
00:49:23,100 --> 00:49:24,600
 unutarnje kohezije u Bojiha.

1343
00:49:24,600 --> 00:49:26,460
 Vijest koju sam pročitao

1344
00:49:26,460 --> 00:49:27,060
 možda jučer,

1345
00:49:27,060 --> 00:49:28,280
 prekuće li vi ste,

1346
00:49:28,280 --> 00:49:30,540
 tiče se rumunskih izbora

1347
00:49:30,540 --> 00:49:31,980
 i onog proruskog kandidata

1348
00:49:31,980 --> 00:49:32,560
 predsjednicu.

1349
00:49:32,560 --> 00:49:34,480
 Kojemu se zabranjuje...

1350
00:49:34,480 --> 00:49:36,160
 Sad, okej, ja znam,

1351
00:49:36,160 --> 00:49:37,160
 suverenista ste,

1352
00:49:37,160 --> 00:49:38,660
 ja malo naginjem tu,

1353
00:49:38,660 --> 00:49:40,320
 ali opet je li to demokratski?

1354
00:49:40,320 --> 00:49:40,960
 Čovjeku se zapravo...

1355
00:49:40,960 --> 00:49:42,180
 Naravno da je nedemokratski.

1356
00:49:42,180 --> 00:49:43,620
 Opet će i zazvat kontraefekt.

1357
00:49:43,620 --> 00:49:44,980
 To je potpuno jasno,

1358
00:49:44,980 --> 00:49:46,460
 ali dakle, naravno da je nedemokratski,

1359
00:49:46,540 --> 00:49:49,480
 jer ako on krši rumunjske zakone,

1360
00:49:49,480 --> 00:49:50,440
 onda protiv njega treba

1361
00:49:50,440 --> 00:49:51,560
 provjeti zakonni postupak,

1362
00:49:51,560 --> 00:49:52,820
 treba ga zatvoriti,

1363
00:49:52,820 --> 00:49:54,600
 ako je zato propisana kazna zatvora.

1364
00:49:54,600 --> 00:49:56,800
 Međutim, ne možete na temelju

1365
00:49:56,800 --> 00:49:58,900
 gole sumnje i na temelju toga

1366
00:49:58,900 --> 00:50:00,800
 što vam ne odgovaraju stajališta

1367
00:50:00,800 --> 00:50:01,760
 koja on zastupa,

1368
00:50:01,760 --> 00:50:03,860
 dakle, isključiti ga od izbora.

1369
00:50:03,860 --> 00:50:04,840
 I to je potpuno jasno

1370
00:50:04,840 --> 00:50:07,020
 da oni koji povlače takve poteze,

1371
00:50:07,020 --> 00:50:08,280
 dakle, koji ga žele isključiti

1372
00:50:08,280 --> 00:50:09,360
 s izbora, zapravo pirlje

1373
00:50:09,360 --> 00:50:10,700
 granu na kojoj sjede.

1374
00:50:11,120 --> 00:50:13,580
 Jedino je pitanje jesu li toga svjesni

1375
00:50:13,580 --> 00:50:16,420
 ili potpuno nesvjesno rade

1376
00:50:16,420 --> 00:50:17,340
 u korist vlastite šte.

1377
00:50:17,340 --> 00:50:18,220
 Da, je li ono tu,

1378
00:50:18,220 --> 00:50:19,780
 ajmo reći mali ljudi obični,

1379
00:50:19,780 --> 00:50:21,380
 mada svi smo mi ljudi isti,

1380
00:50:21,380 --> 00:50:23,280
 s jedne strane, aha,

1381
00:50:23,280 --> 00:50:24,660
 mogu se promeniti spol,

1382
00:50:24,660 --> 00:50:25,480
 nema problema,

1383
00:50:25,480 --> 00:50:26,180
 a s druge strane,

1384
00:50:26,180 --> 00:50:27,660
 okej, čovjek šta bi kažete,

1385
00:50:27,660 --> 00:50:29,020
 ima takve stavove kakve ima,

1386
00:50:29,540 --> 00:50:30,220
 ne možeš se,

1387
00:50:30,220 --> 00:50:31,820
 misli, tu je Evropa,

1388
00:50:31,820 --> 00:50:32,880
 tu je ona,

1389
00:50:32,880 --> 00:50:34,180
 što sam neka smijestila sebe

1390
00:50:34,180 --> 00:50:34,940
 u Magraću klupu.

1391
00:50:34,940 --> 00:50:36,420
 To je onaj paradoks

1392
00:50:36,420 --> 00:50:38,000
 tako zvane liberalne demokracije

1393
00:50:38,000 --> 00:50:39,900
 koja, kao što smo malo prije kazali,

1394
00:50:39,900 --> 00:50:41,480
 dakle, ne dopušta slobodu

1395
00:50:41,480 --> 00:50:42,720
 onima koji su,

1396
00:50:42,720 --> 00:50:44,420
 koji gledaju na stvari drugačije,

1397
00:50:44,420 --> 00:50:45,240
 dakle, dopuštama,

1398
00:50:45,240 --> 00:50:46,920
 mislite različito,

1399
00:50:46,920 --> 00:50:48,660
 ali mislite to u svojoj kući.

1400
00:50:48,660 --> 00:50:49,440
 Dok nekome odgovara, da, da, da.

1401
00:50:49,440 --> 00:50:50,680
 E, mislite to u svome stanu,

1402
00:50:50,680 --> 00:50:51,720
 ali nemojte mi izlezniti van.

1403
00:50:51,720 --> 00:50:52,280
 Da, eto.

1404
00:50:52,600 --> 00:50:53,500
 Znam da vam se žulim,

1405
00:50:53,500 --> 00:50:55,200
 jer još posla nećemo otkrivat kakvoga.

1406
00:50:55,200 --> 00:50:57,820
 Za kraj, očite,

1407
00:50:57,820 --> 00:50:58,900
 mislite još da je opet

1408
00:50:58,900 --> 00:51:00,200
 biti bojkotirani medijima?

1409
00:51:00,200 --> 00:51:02,080
 Misli, sad ste već vi ispisni tu.

1410
00:51:02,080 --> 00:51:03,600
 Ja mislim da blokada

1411
00:51:03,600 --> 00:51:05,060
 onakvog tipa kao što i

1412
00:51:05,060 --> 00:51:06,860
 onakvog intenziteta kao što je bila

1413
00:51:06,860 --> 00:51:08,020
 prošle esene,

1414
00:51:08,020 --> 00:51:08,960
 da više nije moguća.

1415
00:51:08,960 --> 00:51:10,140
 Dakle, sad je, sad,

1416
00:51:10,140 --> 00:51:13,960
 ipak će mi neke stvari biti

1417
00:51:13,960 --> 00:51:15,300
 i neki mediji će biti dostupniji

1418
00:51:15,300 --> 00:51:16,300
 nego što su bili do sad.

1419
00:51:16,300 --> 00:51:17,200
 S druge strane,

1420
00:51:17,200 --> 00:51:19,540
 onima koji su kreirali

1421
00:51:19,540 --> 00:51:20,660
 takvu predložbu

1422
00:51:20,660 --> 00:51:22,460
 i koji su kreirali tu blokadu,

1423
00:51:22,460 --> 00:51:24,760
 sigurno među njima ima i pametnih ljudi

1424
00:51:24,760 --> 00:51:26,160
 koji su slatili da se to ne isplati.

1425
00:51:26,160 --> 00:51:28,300
 Zapravo da je ta medijska blokada

1426
00:51:28,300 --> 00:51:30,180
 meni u jednom dijelu i pomogla.

1427
00:51:30,180 --> 00:51:32,380
 Kao što s jedne strane mi je odmogla,

1428
00:51:32,380 --> 00:51:33,640
 ali je s druge strane i pomogla.

1429
00:51:33,640 --> 00:51:34,560
 Dakle, jer je ona bila,

1430
00:51:34,560 --> 00:51:36,900
 što sam tisuću puta ponovio,

1431
00:51:36,900 --> 00:51:38,140
 dakle, ona je bila potvrda

1432
00:51:38,140 --> 00:51:39,060
 i svjedočba

1433
00:51:39,060 --> 00:51:40,820
 da nisam ničiji plaćenik,

1434
00:51:40,820 --> 00:51:42,000
 da nisam ničiji pouzdanik,

1435
00:51:42,000 --> 00:51:42,920
 da nisam ničiji agent,

1436
00:51:42,920 --> 00:51:43,820
 jer da jesam,

1437
00:51:43,820 --> 00:51:45,640
 onda bi me se pozivalo

1438
00:51:45,640 --> 00:51:47,240
 i u večernji i jutarnji

1439
00:51:47,240 --> 00:51:48,700
 i pozivalo bi se na HTV

1440
00:51:48,700 --> 00:51:50,040
 i koje kakve druge televizije.

1441
00:51:50,040 --> 00:51:51,880
 Znate kakve meni to je smiješno bila?

1442
00:51:51,880 --> 00:51:52,280
 Mislim,

1443
00:51:52,280 --> 00:51:54,220
 aj, relativno se znamo,

1444
00:51:54,220 --> 00:51:56,860
 ali danas stvarno ne možeš nikom

1445
00:51:56,860 --> 00:51:58,420
 ukrasti prostor,

1446
00:51:58,420 --> 00:51:59,560
 svijedokste,

1447
00:51:59,560 --> 00:52:01,100
 mobitel, dva mikrofona,

1448
00:52:01,100 --> 00:52:02,740
 platforme mreže.

1449
00:52:02,740 --> 00:52:04,320
 Mislim, nekoga i...

1450
00:52:04,320 --> 00:52:05,180
 To je apsolutno,

1451
00:52:05,180 --> 00:52:06,120
 kontra, kontra je,

1452
00:52:06,120 --> 00:52:07,500
 to je meni toliko smiješno

1453
00:52:07,500 --> 00:52:08,840
 da sam mora ovo reći.

1454
00:52:08,840 --> 00:52:09,620
 Jasno, ali dakle,

1455
00:52:09,620 --> 00:52:12,300
 prije 35 ili 40 godina je bilo to ono

1456
00:52:12,300 --> 00:52:13,560
 na razini,

1457
00:52:13,560 --> 00:52:14,560
 ali bilo je na razini

1458
00:52:14,560 --> 00:52:15,520
 zaustavite Reuters.

1459
00:52:15,520 --> 00:52:16,780
 Dakle, to je ono

1460
00:52:16,780 --> 00:52:17,740
 u komunizmu bilo

1461
00:52:17,740 --> 00:52:18,560
 zaustavite Reuters,

1462
00:52:18,560 --> 00:52:20,080
 dakle, spriječite objavljivanje,

1463
00:52:20,080 --> 00:52:20,820
 vijesti, ne znam,

1464
00:52:20,820 --> 00:52:22,480
 da se ruši berlinski zid.

1465
00:52:22,480 --> 00:52:23,720
 Može, mogu tomu

1466
00:52:23,720 --> 00:52:24,940
 i oni će ugasiti ovdje,

1467
00:52:24,940 --> 00:52:26,260
 ali neko će drugive tvoriti,

1468
00:52:26,260 --> 00:52:27,160
 tako da...

1469
00:52:27,160 --> 00:52:29,900
 Mislim, želim vam puno sreće,

1470
00:52:30,340 --> 00:52:30,840
 spriha.

1471
00:52:30,840 --> 00:52:33,360
 Krenite s poslom,

1472
00:52:33,360 --> 00:52:34,840
 a mi možemo na kavu.

1473
00:52:34,840 --> 00:52:35,680
 Hvala vam lijep.

1474
00:52:35,680 --> 00:52:36,500
 Ljudi, hvala.

1475
00:52:36,500 --> 00:52:37,580
 Vidimo se, čujemo se.

1476
00:53:00,340 --> 00:53:07,160
 Hvala vam.

